1.	Apt update?
2.	Change weak/default passwords on Accounts, Applications, and services
a.	Usermod
3.	Disable automatic logins for services (ssh, telnet, ftp), and log failed attempts
4.	Disable unneeded services if any
5.	Check permissions on users and files/directories
a.	Sudoers, shadow, group, passwd
6.	Limit apt installs by user
7.	Isolate services
a.	Chroot jail
8.	Set boot loader password




